  "event_preview": "Autopolis International Racing Course is a 4.674 km counter-clockwise permanent road course in Hita City, Ōita Prefecture, Kyushu. Round 3 qualifying was completed on 25 April 2026, but the race was cancelled due to adverse weather. The series will run the rescheduled Round 3 race at Fuji Speedway on 18–19 July 2026 as the second race of a three-race Fuji weekend (alongside the regular Rounds 6 and 7). Qualifying bonus points (3/2/1) for Autopolis were awarded in full; the race itself will be held later at Fuji.",
